message.body: Thought of you. http://blogs.delawareonline.com/pulpculture/2012/09/29/weezer-draws-2000-for-free-christiana-mall-concert/

Yea I just read it . I hadnt before.I'm an android girl with a samsung galaxy

Archaeology with a concentration in gender. I'm studying prehistoric societies!
